title: Seol Hui
description: An old man dies, leaving a large percent of his vast fortune to mysterious girl, Alisa, who has supposedly been abandoned on an island for her entire life. The old man's death becomes Alisa's ticket back into civilization. But as she meets the old man's scheming relatives they begin to wonder if she is much more than a naive country bumpkin. What are her true goals? And who is she really....
